sequenceDiagram
    participant U as Usuário
    participant F as Frontend
    participant B as Backend
    participant S as Stripe
    participant DB as Database

    U->>F: Clica em Assinar Plano
    F->>B: POST /api/stripe/create-checkout
    B->>S: stripe.checkout.sessions.create()
    S-->>B: session.url
    B-->>F: checkout URL
    F->>U: Abre aba Stripe Checkout

    U->>S: Preenche dados e paga
    S->>B: Webhook checkout.session.completed
    B->>DB: updateUserStripeCustomerId()
    B->>DB: upsertSubscription()
    B->>DB: updateCreditsPlan()
    B-->>S: 200 OK

    Note over U,DB: Usuário agora tem créditos do plano

    U->>F: Envia mensagem no chat
    F->>B: SSE /api/chat/stream
    B->>DB: Verifica créditos e limites
    B->>B: Processa com LLM + Tools
    B->>DB: Debita créditos
    B->>DB: Registra uso
    B-->>F: Stream resposta
